1
00:00:12,050 --> 00:00:15,370
[1995]

2
00:00:13,000 --> 00:00:14,400
Come on, guys, over here!

3
00:00:14,830 --> 00:00:16,360
The rain's letting up a bit!

4
00:00:16,520 --> 00:00:17,580
Let's hurry and move

5
00:00:17,580 --> 00:00:21,690
[Jiang Hansheng (Child)]

6
00:00:17,780 --> 00:00:19,260
before it gets heavy again.

7
00:00:19,260 --> 00:00:19,780
Come on.

8
00:00:20,060 --> 00:00:20,660
Turn left.

9
00:00:21,240 --> 00:00:22,100
Be careful!

10
00:00:22,350 --> 00:00:23,870
Turn right!

11
00:00:24,480 --> 00:00:25,670
Let me have a turn!

12
00:00:25,760 --> 00:00:27,620
The road is slippery! Be careful!

13
00:00:27,960 --> 00:00:29,020
Look, everyone,

14
00:00:29,040 --> 00:00:30,300
we have new neighbors!

15
00:00:31,840 --> 00:00:32,170
Here!

16
00:00:32,180 --> 00:00:32,900
Jin, run!

17
00:00:33,200 --> 00:00:33,960
Let's go!

18
00:00:35,080 --> 00:00:35,890
It's my turn!

19
00:00:35,920 --> 00:00:37,580
Jiang Cheng, that's not fair!

20
00:00:38,010 --> 00:00:39,670
What's your name, little one?

21
00:00:39,960 --> 00:00:41,110
My name is Zhou Jin.

22
00:00:42,790 --> 00:00:43,400
Hansheng.

23
00:00:44,270 --> 00:00:46,270
Look how fast that little girl runs.

24
00:00:46,920 --> 00:00:48,590
Her legs are spinning like a windmill.

25
00:00:48,590 --> 00:00:49,350
Not fair!

26
00:00:49,520 --> 00:00:50,470
Not fair!

27
00:00:50,470 --> 00:00:51,860
It's okay, Yan Bin! I'll get it for you!

28
00:00:51,860 --> 00:00:53,390
Come and take it if you dare!

29
00:00:55,660 --> 00:00:56,260
Hansheng,

30
00:00:57,070 --> 00:00:58,360
look how nice it is here.

31
00:00:58,030 --> 00:01:02,130
[Jiang Bozhi, Jiang Hansheng's Father]

32
00:00:58,840 --> 00:00:59,770
Don't you think?

33
00:00:59,840 --> 00:01:00,610
From now on,

34
00:01:00,630 --> 00:01:02,430
you can play with them every day.

35
00:01:03,100 --> 00:01:05,480
Don't just stay cooped up at home
reading books all the time,

36
00:01:05,480 --> 00:01:06,250
okay?

37
00:01:11,470 --> 00:01:12,460
Come on! Come on, guys!

38
00:01:12,460 --> 00:01:13,110
This way!

39
00:01:15,539 --> 00:01:16,570
It's spinning!

40
00:01:17,890 --> 00:01:22,000
[Zhou Jin (Child)]

41
00:02:53,860 --> 00:02:59,829
[Sunsets Secrets Regrets]

42
00:03:00,190 --> 00:03:02,540
[Episode 2]

43
00:03:23,440 --> 00:03:25,370
The security camera is over there.

44
00:03:28,380 --> 00:03:29,600
On the night of the murder,

45
00:03:29,600 --> 00:03:30,620
when the victim took the taxi,

46
00:03:30,620 --> 00:03:32,120
she seemed completely normal.

47
00:03:32,120 --> 00:03:33,160
And that late at night,

48
00:03:33,160 --> 00:03:35,220
going to the suburbs to meet someone—

49
00:03:35,230 --> 00:03:36,950
that person was almost certainly
an acquaintance of hers.

50
00:03:36,950 --> 00:03:38,230
By investigating her social connections,

51
00:03:38,230 --> 00:03:40,000
we'll likely find that person.

52
00:03:41,600 --> 00:03:42,630
She probably had

53
00:03:42,880 --> 00:03:44,780
a more complex social circle than most.

54
00:03:44,780 --> 00:03:45,710
That's strange.

55
00:03:46,250 --> 00:03:47,670
During the time she was missing,

56
00:03:47,670 --> 00:03:49,270
no one reported her absence.

57
00:03:50,230 --> 00:03:51,630
That can only mean the victim

58
00:03:51,630 --> 00:03:52,790
had no relatives or friends

59
00:03:52,790 --> 00:03:53,760
in Haizhou City.

60
00:03:54,200 --> 00:03:55,600
Even when she disappeared,

61
00:03:55,600 --> 00:03:56,440
nobody cared.

62
00:03:57,480 --> 00:03:58,320
No job,

63
00:03:58,350 --> 00:03:59,040
no family.

64
00:03:59,630 --> 00:04:01,160
For such a glamorous woman,

65
00:04:01,480 --> 00:04:03,140
what was her source of income?

66
00:04:05,000 --> 00:04:05,670
Hello.

67
00:04:07,950 --> 00:04:08,390
Hello.

68
00:04:08,440 --> 00:04:12,170
We're from the Criminal Investigation Brigade,
Nancheng Branch.

69
00:04:12,440 --> 00:04:13,200
Do you recognize

70
00:04:13,200 --> 00:04:13,930
this person?

71
00:04:14,670 --> 00:04:15,350
She's dead.

72
00:04:16,200 --> 00:04:17,360
We need you to

73
00:04:17,540 --> 00:04:19,589
truthfully provide all information
about her.

74
00:04:19,589 --> 00:04:20,120
I didn't know her.

75
00:04:20,120 --> 00:04:21,180
I'd never seen her.

76
00:04:21,339 --> 00:04:22,470
You didn't know her?

77
00:04:23,120 --> 00:04:24,270
Take your staff ID

78
00:04:24,840 --> 00:04:25,770
and come with me.

79
00:04:35,370 --> 00:04:36,770
Customizable services.

80
00:04:37,030 --> 00:04:38,030
Is it legitimate?

81
00:04:38,320 --> 00:04:39,320
It's legitimate.

82
00:04:47,400 --> 00:04:49,330
Since she chose this type of hotel,

83
00:04:49,600 --> 00:04:50,770
she probably didn't have

84
00:04:50,770 --> 00:04:51,970
money to spare.

85
00:04:52,890 --> 00:04:53,890
There was

86
00:04:54,190 --> 00:04:55,430
a subtle sexual undertone

87
00:04:55,430 --> 00:04:56,630
in her body language.

88
00:04:57,150 --> 00:04:58,750
She was waiting for her taxi,

89
00:04:58,800 --> 00:05:00,390
but whenever men passed by,

90
00:05:00,640 --> 00:05:02,830
she would instinctively display herself.

91
00:05:02,830 --> 00:05:04,630
Probably a professional habit.

92
00:05:04,800 --> 00:05:06,000
You mean

93
00:05:06,630 --> 00:05:08,000
she was a prostitute?

94
00:05:14,190 --> 00:05:15,650
Quite well-stocked here.

95
00:05:16,990 --> 00:05:17,500
Hello.

96
00:05:18,320 --> 00:05:19,720
Hello, officers. I'm...

97
00:05:19,880 --> 00:05:21,140
the room manager here.

98
00:05:21,150 --> 00:05:22,320
How can I help you?

99
00:05:22,630 --> 00:05:25,290
I'll fully cooperate
with your investigation.

100
00:05:26,860 --> 00:05:27,590
These items?

101
00:05:27,670 --> 00:05:29,070
They're just promotional items.

102
00:05:29,070 --> 00:05:29,950
Some guests

103
00:05:29,950 --> 00:05:31,080
have certain needs,

104
00:05:31,090 --> 00:05:31,850
so they buy these things here—

105
00:05:31,850 --> 00:05:34,050
it saves them a trip to the supermarket.

106
00:05:36,800 --> 00:05:38,060
Skip the formalities.

107
00:05:39,070 --> 00:05:41,120
Do you typically procure prostitutes

108
00:05:41,120 --> 00:05:43,450
or just provide venues for prostitution?

109
00:05:44,350 --> 00:05:45,950
You must be joking, officer.

110
00:05:52,120 --> 00:05:53,150
Are you her boss

111
00:05:53,950 --> 00:05:54,810
or her partner?

112
00:05:56,560 --> 00:05:57,590
I don't know her.

113
00:05:58,020 --> 00:05:58,659
I don't.

114
00:06:01,130 --> 00:06:02,930
No one can keep secrets forever.

115
00:06:03,070 --> 00:06:04,400
When people won't talk,

116
00:06:04,860 --> 00:06:07,060
their fingers can still tell the story.

117
00:06:07,800 --> 00:06:08,630
So can toes.

118
00:06:09,860 --> 00:06:11,660
You really have a sense of humor.

119
00:06:12,100 --> 00:06:13,120
Wasting our time

120
00:06:13,150 --> 00:06:14,350
won't do you any good.

121
00:06:14,960 --> 00:06:16,560
The girl in the photo is dead.

122
00:06:17,290 --> 00:06:18,220
This is serious.

123
00:06:18,820 --> 00:06:20,280
I'll ask you one last time:

124
00:06:20,390 --> 00:06:21,660
do you know her or not?

125
00:06:24,390 --> 00:06:25,250
Won't talk, eh?

126
00:06:25,630 --> 00:06:27,660
Let's continue
this conversation elsewhere.

127
00:06:27,660 --> 00:06:28,340
Meng Ling.

128
00:06:28,470 --> 00:06:29,690
Her name was Meng Ling.

129
00:06:29,690 --> 00:06:30,890
I knew her, I knew her.

130
00:06:33,800 --> 00:06:35,000
That night, Meng Ling

131
00:06:35,070 --> 00:06:35,680
was supposed to

132
00:06:35,680 --> 00:06:37,470
meet a pimp named Lai San.

133
00:06:38,200 --> 00:06:40,030
Meng Ling must have had

134
00:06:40,030 --> 00:06:41,159
some dirt on Lai San,

135
00:06:41,400 --> 00:06:42,140
using it to threaten him,

136
00:06:42,140 --> 00:06:44,159
and that's what got her into trouble.

137
00:06:44,159 --> 00:06:45,880
We have already issued a statement.

138
00:06:45,880 --> 00:06:46,880
They all knew her.

139
00:06:47,070 --> 00:06:48,400
Why did no one report it?

140
00:06:48,530 --> 00:06:50,240
Because on the 23rd, Meng Ling

141
00:06:50,240 --> 00:06:51,370
told the hotel staff

142
00:06:51,510 --> 00:06:52,710
that she was going back to her hometown

143
00:06:52,710 --> 00:06:54,040
and would never return.

144
00:06:54,300 --> 00:06:55,440
She must have been really confident

145
00:06:55,440 --> 00:06:56,470
that she could settle things

146
00:06:56,470 --> 00:06:57,680
with Lai San

147
00:06:57,680 --> 00:06:58,880
and return to her hometown smoothly.

148
00:06:58,880 --> 00:07:00,400
So even when something happened to her,

149
00:07:00,400 --> 00:07:03,150
the hotel staff just assumed
she went back to her hometown.

150
00:07:03,150 --> 00:07:04,680
What's Lai San's real name?

151
00:07:05,030 --> 00:07:06,030
We don't know yet.

152
00:07:06,560 --> 00:07:08,420
We only know that's his nickname.

153
00:07:08,830 --> 00:07:10,360
But he told the hotel staff

154
00:07:10,680 --> 00:07:12,940
that his cousin was about to
open a new bar

155
00:07:13,200 --> 00:07:15,460
and that he would manage it in the future.

156
00:07:15,570 --> 00:07:17,170
It's opening tonight at 8 PM.

157
00:07:17,290 --> 00:07:18,290
The bar's name is

158
00:07:18,600 --> 00:07:21,090
[Phoenix Fire Bar]

159
00:07:19,480 --> 00:07:20,280
Phoenix Fire.

160
00:07:28,440 --> 00:07:30,570
Meng Ling was killed several days ago.

161
00:07:30,950 --> 00:07:32,270
We can't rule out the possibility

162
00:07:32,270 --> 00:07:34,320
that Lai San has already fled
to avoid punishment.

163
00:07:34,320 --> 00:07:34,880
So

164
00:07:34,950 --> 00:07:36,150
tonight's operation

165
00:07:36,560 --> 00:07:38,030
is not just to find Lai San

166
00:07:38,390 --> 00:07:39,320
but also to find

167
00:07:39,800 --> 00:07:40,630
his cousin,

168
00:07:40,950 --> 00:07:41,470
He Wu.

169
00:07:43,950 --> 00:07:44,680
Zhou Jin.

170
00:07:45,470 --> 00:07:47,000
Go check the private rooms.

171
00:07:48,100 --> 00:07:48,780
Roger that.

172
00:07:49,570 --> 00:07:51,030
He Wu's business dealings

173
00:07:51,030 --> 00:07:52,320
are mostly illegal.

174
00:07:52,590 --> 00:07:54,240
We have been watching him for a long time,

175
00:07:54,240 --> 00:07:56,510
but we haven't found solid evidence yet.

176
00:07:57,030 --> 00:07:58,000
If Meng Ling

177
00:07:58,030 --> 00:07:59,760
was indeed killed by Lai San,

178
00:08:00,060 --> 00:08:00,570
then

179
00:08:00,790 --> 00:08:02,030
we have to suspect

180
00:08:02,140 --> 00:08:03,410
that He Wu

181
00:08:04,030 --> 00:08:04,680
knew about

182
00:08:05,120 --> 00:08:06,390
the gun.

183
00:08:09,620 --> 00:08:10,970
Please stop hitting me!

184
00:08:11,830 --> 00:08:13,160
I can't take it anymore!

185
00:08:13,680 --> 00:08:14,950
I'll never do it again!

186
00:08:15,120 --> 00:08:15,710
Cheng!

187
00:08:16,360 --> 00:08:17,620
Just chop off one of his hands.

188
00:08:17,620 --> 00:08:19,200
Let's see if he dares to do it again!

189
00:08:19,200 --> 00:08:20,440
Don't chop off my hand.

190
00:08:20,440 --> 00:08:21,080
Cheng,

191
00:08:21,380 --> 00:08:23,170
I really know I was wrong.

192
00:08:23,200 --> 00:08:24,360
Please stop hitting me!

193
00:08:24,360 --> 00:08:25,480
I'm begging you!

194
00:08:25,870 --> 00:08:27,750
We keep you around to work for us,

195
00:08:27,910 --> 00:08:29,310
and you, little bastard,

196
00:08:29,590 --> 00:08:31,790
dare to steal from us to sell on your own?

197
00:08:38,350 --> 00:08:39,590
I needed money!

198
00:08:39,590 --> 00:08:40,919
My mother is sick!

199
00:08:41,330 --> 00:08:43,000
I really needed the money!

200
00:08:43,490 --> 00:08:44,830
Cheng, I promise

201
00:08:45,350 --> 00:08:46,920
I'll work like a dog

202
00:08:46,920 --> 00:08:48,400
and pay you back every cent!

203
00:08:48,400 --> 00:08:49,730
Please stop hitting me!

204
00:08:51,160 --> 00:08:52,000
Help me!

205
00:08:52,030 --> 00:08:53,070
Help!

206
00:08:53,090 --> 00:08:55,050
Someone, please help me!

207
00:08:56,760 --> 00:08:58,220
They're beating him so badly.

208
00:08:58,220 --> 00:08:59,410
What should we do, sis?

209
00:08:59,410 --> 00:09:00,350
Let's go, quickly.

210
00:09:00,350 --> 00:09:00,830
Leave it alone.

211
00:09:00,830 --> 00:09:01,710
It's none of our business.

212
00:09:01,710 --> 00:09:03,280
Don't get yourself in trouble.

213
00:09:03,280 --> 00:09:04,610
I can't take it anymore!

214
00:09:10,590 --> 00:09:11,830
Stop hitting me!

215
00:09:11,850 --> 00:09:14,330
I needed money! My mother is sick!

216
00:09:14,870 --> 00:09:16,840
I really needed the money!

217
00:09:18,460 --> 00:09:19,060
Chief Tan,

218
00:09:19,320 --> 00:09:22,000
it sounds like people are fighting
in the storage room.

219
00:09:22,000 --> 00:09:22,840
Don't worry.

220
00:09:23,200 --> 00:09:24,130
Leave it for now.

221
00:09:24,410 --> 00:09:25,980
I'll send Wu to check it out.

222
00:09:26,610 --> 00:09:27,160
Roger.

223
00:09:29,790 --> 00:09:31,390
Help!

224
00:09:32,440 --> 00:09:34,990
Is anyone there to help me?

225
00:09:36,510 --> 00:09:39,320
Is anyone there to help me?

226
00:09:41,830 --> 00:09:42,440
Continue!

227
00:09:42,550 --> 00:09:43,260
Stop!

228
00:09:44,280 --> 00:09:45,340
What are you doing?

229
00:09:45,660 --> 00:09:46,320
Having fun.

230
00:09:47,280 --> 00:09:47,940
Having fun?

231
00:09:54,190 --> 00:09:54,920
Are you okay?

232
00:09:55,520 --> 00:09:56,760
Do you need me to call the police?

233
00:09:56,760 --> 00:09:58,760
Where did this nosy woman come from?

234
00:09:59,390 --> 00:10:00,720
Mind your own business.

235
00:10:01,190 --> 00:10:01,720
Get lost!

236
00:10:03,310 --> 00:10:05,950
You should treat a lady
with basic respect.

237
00:10:07,670 --> 00:10:10,940
[Jiang Cheng,
Vice President of Hengyun Logistics]

238
00:10:13,430 --> 00:10:15,360
What a beautiful lady.

239
00:10:25,030 --> 00:10:25,680
Bleach,

240
00:10:26,400 --> 00:10:27,520
you're lucky today.

241
00:10:27,520 --> 00:10:28,920
You've met a good person.

242
00:10:29,710 --> 00:10:31,770
Since this pretty lady is so curious,

243
00:10:31,980 --> 00:10:34,440
you'd better answer her question properly.

244
00:10:34,990 --> 00:10:35,520
I...

245
00:10:35,830 --> 00:10:37,590
don't need you to call the police.

246
00:10:37,590 --> 00:10:38,590
Did you hear that?

247
00:10:39,440 --> 00:10:40,950
Wanna have some fun

248
00:10:42,040 --> 00:10:42,880
with us?

249
00:10:44,920 --> 00:10:45,470
Get lost.

250
00:10:46,120 --> 00:10:47,640
She's quite feisty.

251
00:10:50,280 --> 00:10:50,830
Bleach,

252
00:10:51,070 --> 00:10:52,530
I'll give you two options:

253
00:10:52,640 --> 00:10:53,110
one,

254
00:10:53,690 --> 00:10:54,340
you leave,

255
00:10:55,200 --> 00:10:56,660
and this young lady stays.

256
00:10:56,710 --> 00:10:57,200
Two,

257
00:10:57,710 --> 00:10:58,970
the young lady leaves,

258
00:10:58,990 --> 00:10:59,800
and you stay.

259
00:11:00,560 --> 00:11:01,180
Choice!

260
00:11:08,790 --> 00:11:11,440
You brought this on yourself by meddling.

261
00:11:11,610 --> 00:11:13,940
You brought this on yourself by meddling.

262
00:11:18,990 --> 00:11:19,750
Miss,

263
00:11:20,330 --> 00:11:21,280
look at you,

264
00:11:21,670 --> 00:11:23,270
standing up for such a loser.

265
00:11:23,280 --> 00:11:24,080
Is it worth it?

266
00:11:27,770 --> 00:11:28,950
This chick's got some fire.

267
00:11:28,950 --> 00:11:29,480
Get lost!

268
00:11:30,950 --> 00:11:31,880
Get out of my way.

269
00:11:38,640 --> 00:11:39,770
Out on duty, are you?

270
00:11:41,110 --> 00:11:42,640
Who are you investigating?

271
00:11:43,910 --> 00:11:46,170
I know police tactics better than you do.

272
00:11:46,280 --> 00:11:47,320
Investigate all you want,

273
00:11:47,320 --> 00:11:49,980
but why stick your nose
where it doesn't belong?

274
00:11:50,320 --> 00:11:51,320
It's been 2 years.

275
00:11:52,130 --> 00:11:53,260
You're still alive.

276
00:11:54,240 --> 00:11:55,770
Wishing me dead that badly?

277
00:11:56,970 --> 00:11:58,630
I've missed you all this time.

278
00:11:58,950 --> 00:11:59,950
If I'm going to die,

279
00:11:59,950 --> 00:12:01,480
I'd rather die on top of you.

280
00:12:03,980 --> 00:12:04,640
Let go of me.

281
00:12:05,680 --> 00:12:06,320
Jin.

282
00:12:06,610 --> 00:12:08,040
You've really lost your touch.

283
00:12:08,040 --> 00:12:10,160
Don't ever tell people I trained you.

284
00:12:10,800 --> 00:12:11,640
Let go of me!

285
00:12:11,680 --> 00:12:12,520
What a temper.

286
00:12:12,720 --> 00:12:14,470
I was just messing with you,
and you're actually getting mad?

287
00:12:14,470 --> 00:12:15,130
Don't move!

288
00:12:16,680 --> 00:12:18,080
Let me take a closer look.

289
00:12:38,710 --> 00:12:40,310
You've really changed a lot.

290
00:12:41,990 --> 00:12:43,720
Why did you grow your hair long?

291
00:12:43,830 --> 00:12:45,490
Short hair suited you better.

292
00:12:45,520 --> 00:12:47,450
You're the one who's changed a lot.

293
00:12:47,960 --> 00:12:49,560
Jiang Cheng is already dead.

294
00:12:50,640 --> 00:12:51,400
Who are you?

295
00:12:58,280 --> 00:12:59,940
You're being so harsh with me.

296
00:13:03,750 --> 00:13:04,590
Don't forget.

297
00:13:05,580 --> 00:13:08,510
I'm probably the only one
who busted my own boyfriend

298
00:13:08,750 --> 00:13:11,040
during an anti-prostitution crackdown.

299
00:13:11,040 --> 00:13:13,820
[2012]

300
00:13:51,710 --> 00:13:54,110
If I catch any more evidence
of your crimes,

301
00:13:55,120 --> 00:13:56,850
I definitely won't let you off.

302
00:13:59,410 --> 00:14:00,470
-Jin...
-Get lost!

303
00:14:52,230 --> 00:14:53,890
We might have found the 3,000.

304
00:15:00,780 --> 00:15:01,870
Lai San

305
00:15:01,870 --> 00:15:04,470
has a very distinctive tattoo
on his right arm.

306
00:15:22,210 --> 00:15:24,140
I left the 3,000 at the bar counter.

307
00:15:24,870 --> 00:15:25,600
Bar counter!

308
00:15:25,750 --> 00:15:26,230
Move in!

309
00:15:45,610 --> 00:15:46,880
He's leaving, he's leaving.

310
00:15:46,880 --> 00:15:47,960
Zhou Jin, Zhou Jin,

311
00:15:47,990 --> 00:15:48,950
don't rush.

312
00:15:49,160 --> 00:15:50,420
You're still injured!

313
00:15:50,440 --> 00:15:51,970
Wait for the tactical team!

314
00:16:07,390 --> 00:16:08,250
Tactical team,

315
00:16:08,320 --> 00:16:09,550
surround the entire alley.

316
00:16:09,550 --> 00:16:10,980
Block both ends.

317
00:16:19,740 --> 00:16:21,270
There really are cops here.

318
00:16:23,790 --> 00:16:24,710
Are you Lai San?

319
00:16:25,920 --> 00:16:27,180
It's none of your business.

320
00:16:27,180 --> 00:16:28,240
Who are you anyway?

321
00:16:28,600 --> 00:16:30,360
Do you know whose turf this is?

322
00:16:30,630 --> 00:16:32,240
My cousin's bar just opened today,

323
00:16:32,240 --> 00:16:33,200
and you come to cause trouble?

324
00:16:33,200 --> 00:16:34,580
You did this on purpose, didn't you?

325
00:16:34,580 --> 00:16:35,220
Get her!

326
00:17:22,599 --> 00:17:23,270
Don't move!

327
00:17:23,359 --> 00:17:24,010
Freeze!

328
00:17:24,319 --> 00:17:24,910
Freeze!

329
00:17:25,390 --> 00:17:26,050
Don't move!

330
00:17:26,460 --> 00:17:26,970
Get down!

331
00:17:26,970 --> 00:17:27,569
Come down!

332
00:17:28,790 --> 00:17:29,720
Are you alright?

333
00:17:30,080 --> 00:17:30,540
I'm fine.

334
00:17:30,540 --> 00:17:31,200
Don't move!

335
00:17:33,670 --> 00:17:34,280
Cuff him!

336
00:17:53,450 --> 00:17:54,380
Why are you here?

337
00:17:56,080 --> 00:17:57,410
Class was rescheduled.

338
00:17:57,740 --> 00:17:58,470
Are you okay?

339
00:17:58,780 --> 00:17:59,450
I'm fine.

340
00:18:01,220 --> 00:18:01,790
Zhou Jin!

341
00:18:03,360 --> 00:18:05,600
Have you forgotten
your ribs are still injured?

342
00:18:05,600 --> 00:18:07,470
Didn't I tell you not to go in?

343
00:18:07,680 --> 00:18:08,870
I told you to wait for the tactical team.

344
00:18:08,870 --> 00:18:09,960
I told you!

345
00:18:10,160 --> 00:18:11,010
Why were you showing off?

346
00:18:11,010 --> 00:18:12,320
If I didn't chase him,
he would've escaped.

347
00:18:12,320 --> 00:18:13,380
Where could he run?

348
00:18:13,750 --> 00:18:14,920
We had him surrounded.

349
00:18:14,920 --> 00:18:15,960
Where could he possibly go?

350
00:18:15,960 --> 00:18:17,420
What, did he sprout wings?

351
00:18:18,600 --> 00:18:19,200
Chief Tan,

352
00:18:19,710 --> 00:18:21,750
-Zhou Jin did it for...
-Professor Jiang.

353
00:18:21,750 --> 00:18:23,030
I'm disciplining my subordinate.

354
00:18:23,030 --> 00:18:24,030
Please excuse us.

355
00:18:25,210 --> 00:18:25,610
Right,

356
00:18:26,240 --> 00:18:26,990
get in the car,

357
00:18:26,990 --> 00:18:29,320
and get that arm wound treated right away.

358
00:18:41,300 --> 00:18:43,700
Stop thinking you're such a great fighter.

359
00:18:44,340 --> 00:18:46,120
Did you follow my instructions?

360
00:18:46,120 --> 00:18:47,230
Did I give orders?

361
00:18:48,140 --> 00:18:49,940
You got lucky this time.

362
00:18:50,230 --> 00:18:51,430
What about next time?

363
00:18:52,050 --> 00:18:52,980
I'm telling you,

364
00:18:53,020 --> 00:18:54,480
if something happens to you,

365
00:18:54,480 --> 00:18:56,540
at least you'd die in the line of duty!

366
00:18:57,280 --> 00:18:58,950
But what if innocent bystanders
get involved and end up hurt?

367
00:18:58,950 --> 00:19:01,280
That would be a needless tragedy for them!

368
00:19:01,340 --> 00:19:02,740
You're a police officer.

369
00:19:03,390 --> 00:19:05,190
Who is supposed to protect whom?

370
00:19:07,170 --> 00:19:09,050
Go back and write a self-criticism report!

371
00:19:09,050 --> 00:19:09,640
Yes, sir.

372
00:19:11,720 --> 00:19:12,580
What about him?

373
00:19:16,710 --> 00:19:17,710
I know, I know.

374
00:19:18,550 --> 00:19:19,470
Write down the entire process

375
00:19:19,470 --> 00:19:20,840
in complete detail.

376
00:19:22,020 --> 00:19:24,400
Including the part where you took off
your earpiece and acted on your own.

377
00:19:24,400 --> 00:19:24,920
Also,

378
00:19:25,470 --> 00:19:27,160
when you go undercover in the future,

379
00:19:27,160 --> 00:19:28,300
don't wear just anything.

380
00:19:28,300 --> 00:19:29,960
What on earth are you wearing?

381
00:19:31,230 --> 00:19:31,960
Are you done?

382
00:19:31,990 --> 00:19:32,880
-Yes, sir!
-Yes, sir!

383
00:19:32,880 --> 00:19:33,550
Take them away!

384
00:19:33,550 --> 00:19:34,750
-Yes, sir!
-Yes, sir!

385
00:19:35,670 --> 00:19:36,200
Move!

386
00:19:37,950 --> 00:19:38,400
Move!

387
00:19:38,980 --> 00:19:39,980
Behave yourself!

388
00:19:46,430 --> 00:19:48,120
I'll kill you when I get out.

389
00:19:48,140 --> 00:19:48,390
Move!

390
00:19:48,390 --> 00:19:49,120
Keep moving!

391
00:19:54,040 --> 00:19:55,240
What did you just say?

392
00:19:55,290 --> 00:19:56,050
I said,

393
00:19:56,720 --> 00:19:58,240
I'll finish her.

394
00:20:00,080 --> 00:20:00,670
Professor Jiang!

395
00:20:00,670 --> 00:20:00,990
Professor Jiang!

396
00:20:00,990 --> 00:20:01,580
Professor Jiang!

397
00:20:01,580 --> 00:20:02,710
Mind your behavior!

398
00:20:02,710 --> 00:20:03,440
Please control yourself!

399
00:20:03,440 --> 00:20:04,030
Everyone, look!

400
00:20:04,030 --> 00:20:05,300
The police are beating me!

401
00:20:05,300 --> 00:20:07,470
Look! The police are beating me!

402
00:20:07,540 --> 00:20:07,910
Move.

403
00:20:07,940 --> 00:20:08,590
Move!

404
00:20:09,250 --> 00:20:09,730
Move!

405
00:20:17,640 --> 00:20:18,240
Hansheng.

406
00:20:22,470 --> 00:20:23,600
Professor Jiang...

407
00:20:25,030 --> 00:20:26,140
why did you do that?

408
00:20:26,190 --> 00:20:26,790
Chief Tan,

409
00:20:28,310 --> 00:20:29,370
Lai San's left hand

410
00:20:29,550 --> 00:20:30,810
has no strength at all.

411
00:20:31,600 --> 00:20:32,350
He alone

412
00:20:32,550 --> 00:20:33,470
couldn't possibly have

413
00:20:33,470 --> 00:20:35,800
carried out the murder and body disposal.

414
00:20:35,880 --> 00:20:38,310
I suspect there was a third person
at the scene.

415
00:20:38,310 --> 00:20:39,200
We need to

416
00:20:39,230 --> 00:20:41,090
interrogate his men separately.

417
00:20:43,770 --> 00:20:45,640
So that was your purpose just now?

418
00:20:48,780 --> 00:20:49,270
No.

419
00:20:50,140 --> 00:20:51,670
I really did want to hit him.

420
00:21:48,360 --> 00:21:49,310
Open up! Open up!

421
00:21:50,470 --> 00:21:52,270
We're from the Nancheng Branch.

422
00:22:09,710 --> 00:22:10,470
Chief Tan,

423
00:22:10,850 --> 00:22:11,880
we've arrested Lai San's men.

424
00:22:11,880 --> 00:22:13,900
Should we bring them directly
to your precinct?

425
00:22:13,900 --> 00:22:15,700
Okay. Thanks for your hard work.

426
00:22:16,330 --> 00:22:17,270
I know the law too.

427
00:22:17,270 --> 00:22:17,860
I know.

428
00:22:18,250 --> 00:22:20,210
You can only detain me for 48 hours.

429
00:22:20,920 --> 00:22:22,800
When time's up and you've got no evidence,

430
00:22:22,800 --> 00:22:24,950
you'll have to respectfully send me home.

431
00:22:24,950 --> 00:22:25,550
Otherwise,

432
00:22:25,550 --> 00:22:28,810
I'll file a complaint against you
at the municipal bureau.

433
00:22:28,950 --> 00:22:29,800
Dream on.

434
00:22:30,290 --> 00:22:32,150
Setting Meng Ling's case aside for now—

435
00:22:32,150 --> 00:22:34,320
just for the charge of
organizing prostitution alone,

436
00:22:34,320 --> 00:22:35,320
you won't get out.

437
00:22:39,190 --> 00:22:40,000
No, no, no,

438
00:22:40,300 --> 00:22:41,500
my arm hurts too much.

439
00:22:41,720 --> 00:22:42,180
Listen,

440
00:22:42,250 --> 00:22:43,190
I need to go to the hospital.

441
00:22:43,190 --> 00:22:44,110
I really need medical attention!

442
00:22:44,110 --> 00:22:46,080
Your guy was way too rough!

443
00:22:46,080 --> 00:22:47,480
He could've crippled me!

444
00:22:47,600 --> 00:22:48,730
I'm going to sue him!

445
00:22:49,040 --> 00:22:49,770
Don't worry.

446
00:22:50,540 --> 00:22:51,930
The doctor is on his way.

447
00:22:52,240 --> 00:22:53,820
We'll have you thoroughly examined.

448
00:22:53,820 --> 00:22:54,310
Besides,

449
00:22:54,310 --> 00:22:56,030
we've checked your medical records

450
00:22:56,030 --> 00:22:57,970
in the City Central Hospital system.

451
00:22:57,970 --> 00:22:58,700
One year ago,

452
00:22:58,760 --> 00:22:59,760
you were in a fight

453
00:22:59,890 --> 00:23:01,220
and broke your left arm.

454
00:23:01,310 --> 00:23:03,780
After it healed,
though it didn't affect your daily life,

455
00:23:03,780 --> 00:23:04,610
your left hand

456
00:23:04,670 --> 00:23:06,220
couldn't lift heavy objects anymore.

457
00:23:06,220 --> 00:23:07,220
Isn't that right?

458
00:23:07,600 --> 00:23:08,460
Lai Zhengtian.

459
00:23:09,100 --> 00:23:10,100
Trying to fool us?

460
00:23:10,520 --> 00:23:11,780
It's not going to work.

461
00:23:13,360 --> 00:23:14,250
He Wu.

462
00:23:15,290 --> 00:23:16,010
Mr. He.

463
00:23:16,770 --> 00:23:17,850
Boss He!

464
00:23:18,270 --> 00:23:19,530
No, no, you flatter me.

465
00:23:19,750 --> 00:23:20,670
Just call me He Wu.

466
00:23:20,670 --> 00:23:22,190
Surname He, given name Wu.

467
00:23:23,760 --> 00:23:25,960
What's your relationship with Lai San?

468
00:23:26,190 --> 00:23:28,430
You mean... Lai Zhengtian, right?

469
00:23:28,810 --> 00:23:29,290
Yes.

470
00:23:29,870 --> 00:23:30,730
Lai Zhengtian.

471
00:23:31,520 --> 00:23:32,580
My distant cousin.

472
00:23:32,880 --> 00:23:33,880
A distant cousin.

473
00:23:34,030 --> 00:23:35,030
What stake

474
00:23:35,310 --> 00:23:36,970
does this cousin of yours hold

475
00:23:37,270 --> 00:23:39,000
in Hengyun Logistics Company?

476
00:23:39,390 --> 00:23:40,190
Five percent.

477
00:23:41,390 --> 00:23:42,720
What exactly does he do?

478
00:23:43,750 --> 00:23:45,470
What can he do?

479
00:23:46,630 --> 00:23:47,670
He's family.

480
00:23:48,130 --> 00:23:49,090
Lai San... oh no,

481
00:23:49,840 --> 00:23:50,710
Lai Zhengtian.

482
00:23:51,170 --> 00:23:53,060
He's idle all day,

483
00:23:53,130 --> 00:23:54,120
can't hold down a regular job,

484
00:23:54,120 --> 00:23:55,720
and can't do any proper work.

485
00:23:56,070 --> 00:23:58,250
Out of respect
for our family relationship,

486
00:23:58,250 --> 00:24:01,250
I just find an excuse
to give him some living expenses.

487
00:24:01,290 --> 00:24:02,270
Understandable.

488
00:24:02,270 --> 00:24:03,270
Understandable.

489
00:24:04,400 --> 00:24:06,130
What about his other business?

490
00:24:07,050 --> 00:24:08,680
He has other business?

491
00:24:10,150 --> 00:24:11,880
I really don't know about that.

492
00:24:12,380 --> 00:24:13,780
Well, Mr. Lai,

493
00:24:13,980 --> 00:24:15,170
for him, this sex trade

494
00:24:15,170 --> 00:24:17,030
isn't mainly about making money.

495
00:24:17,080 --> 00:24:18,950
It's mainly about having us girls

496
00:24:19,090 --> 00:24:20,330
please the guys

497
00:24:20,360 --> 00:24:21,750
and make the big shots happy.

498
00:24:21,750 --> 00:24:22,270
Get it?

499
00:24:23,190 --> 00:24:24,190
Be more specific.

500
00:24:24,480 --> 00:24:25,480
Please whom?

501
00:24:25,840 --> 00:24:27,170
I dare not tell you that.

502
00:24:27,400 --> 00:24:29,470
I'm already in enough trouble.

503
00:24:29,500 --> 00:24:30,680
I don't want to lose my life.

504
00:24:30,680 --> 00:24:32,960
You can forget about getting out of here.

505
00:24:33,430 --> 00:24:35,800
Just tell us how Meng Ling died.

506
00:24:35,820 --> 00:24:37,140
Save everyone's time!

507
00:24:38,920 --> 00:24:39,920
She was just a bitch.

508
00:24:39,920 --> 00:24:41,720
It wouldn't be a pity if she died.

509
00:24:41,820 --> 00:24:43,480
But I had nothing to do with it.

510
00:24:45,600 --> 00:24:46,230
Well,

511
00:24:46,310 --> 00:24:47,000
Mr. He,

512
00:24:47,830 --> 00:24:50,630
you can't pretend not to know
what's going on here.

513
00:24:51,330 --> 00:24:52,440
No, of course not.

514
00:24:52,780 --> 00:24:55,040
How could I still play dumb at this point?

515
00:24:56,570 --> 00:24:58,080
I was just sleeping at home that day.

516
00:24:58,080 --> 00:24:59,210
Didn't go anywhere.

517
00:24:59,380 --> 00:25:00,310
Who can prove it?

518
00:25:00,790 --> 00:25:01,850
My bed can prove it.

519
00:25:02,000 --> 00:25:03,260
Are you messing with us?

520
00:25:03,260 --> 00:25:03,930
Be honest!

521
00:25:05,080 --> 00:25:06,610
What could I possibly know?

522
00:25:06,640 --> 00:25:07,880
I'm just a nobody.

523
00:25:08,430 --> 00:25:09,490
You helped him open

524
00:25:09,840 --> 00:25:11,300
Phoenix Fire, didn't you?

525
00:25:11,410 --> 00:25:14,020
How could I have
opened Phoenix Fire for him?

526
00:25:14,880 --> 00:25:16,790
Phoenix Fire is
a legitimate establishment.

527
00:25:16,790 --> 00:25:18,750
We have a proper business license

528
00:25:18,770 --> 00:25:19,910
and an official organizational structure.

529
00:25:19,910 --> 00:25:20,470
We're...

530
00:25:20,670 --> 00:25:21,940
We're running a legitimate business.

531
00:25:21,940 --> 00:25:24,400
Whether it's legitimate or not,
we'll see later.

532
00:25:24,400 --> 00:25:25,260
First, tell me,

533
00:25:25,800 --> 00:25:28,040
who's really in charge of Phoenix Fire?

534
00:25:29,550 --> 00:25:31,880
Strictly speaking, Phoenix Fire is

535
00:25:32,890 --> 00:25:35,450
now fully managed by Jiang Cheng.

536
00:25:35,800 --> 00:25:36,330
It has...

537
00:25:36,520 --> 00:25:38,920
has nothing to do
with Lai Zhengtian at all.

538
00:25:41,150 --> 00:25:42,110
Lai Zhengtian.

539
00:25:42,980 --> 00:25:45,710
We're giving you a chance
by letting you confess.

540
00:25:45,760 --> 00:25:47,000
What chance?

541
00:25:48,150 --> 00:25:49,350
Do you have evidence?

542
00:25:50,040 --> 00:25:51,440
If you have evidence, I'll admit it.

543
00:25:51,440 --> 00:25:52,570
Do you have any?

544
00:26:04,000 --> 00:26:05,130
I'll get some sleep.

545
00:26:14,680 --> 00:26:15,680
If I tell you...

546
00:26:17,080 --> 00:26:18,480
can you take down Lai San?

547
00:26:21,840 --> 00:26:23,630
As long as the evidence is solid,

548
00:26:23,630 --> 00:26:25,310
we won't let any criminal

549
00:26:25,330 --> 00:26:26,370
escape justice.

550
00:26:27,030 --> 00:26:28,160
Well, by that logic,

551
00:26:29,910 --> 00:26:32,440
there wouldn't be any bad people
in the world.

552
00:26:33,870 --> 00:26:34,600
That's true.

553
00:26:35,270 --> 00:26:36,670
Lai San isn't even human.

554
00:26:37,410 --> 00:26:38,780
He's just a dog.

555
00:26:39,310 --> 00:26:41,030
A filthy dog, a mad dog!

556
00:26:42,390 --> 00:26:43,390
Meng Ling is dead.

557
00:26:44,110 --> 00:26:45,440
He must have killed her.

558
00:26:45,750 --> 00:26:46,880
Why are you so sure?

559
00:26:47,620 --> 00:26:49,800
Meng Ling was from a village in Honglian

560
00:26:49,800 --> 00:26:51,600
and didn't have much schooling.

561
00:26:51,790 --> 00:26:53,400
Her pride was her undoing.

562
00:26:54,780 --> 00:26:56,240
It was also her bad luck...

563
00:26:58,360 --> 00:27:00,220
to meet Lai San, that cunning fox.

564
00:27:00,720 --> 00:27:03,450
Even nine lives
wouldn't be enough for his games.

565
00:27:03,650 --> 00:27:05,780
Lai San gave her some brand-name bags.

566
00:27:05,960 --> 00:27:07,620
They were all fake, actually.

567
00:27:08,670 --> 00:27:09,870
She got carried away.

568
00:27:10,800 --> 00:27:12,450
Thought she'd met someone
who could help her

569
00:27:12,450 --> 00:27:14,110
and that she could make it big.

570
00:27:14,950 --> 00:27:16,080
What happened next?

571
00:27:17,790 --> 00:27:19,420
After Lai San won her over...

572
00:27:22,180 --> 00:27:24,090
that very night, he brought several men,

573
00:27:24,090 --> 00:27:25,490
and they gang-raped her.

574
00:27:26,750 --> 00:27:29,150
How could a young girl like her
handle that?

575
00:27:29,180 --> 00:27:30,710
Lai San was truly ruthless—

576
00:27:31,180 --> 00:27:32,950
he forced her to prostitute herself

577
00:27:32,950 --> 00:27:35,010
and beat her severely every few days.

578
00:27:35,410 --> 00:27:36,410
And then later...

579
00:27:39,010 --> 00:27:40,140
About two years ago,

580
00:27:41,610 --> 00:27:42,400
Boss He—

581
00:27:43,040 --> 00:27:44,080
Lai San's cousin,

582
00:27:44,320 --> 00:27:44,910
He Wu—

583
00:27:45,400 --> 00:27:46,430
had a man

584
00:27:47,190 --> 00:27:48,800
working for him named Cheng.

585
00:27:49,840 --> 00:27:51,640
This guy Cheng was very capable.

586
00:27:52,120 --> 00:27:53,400
Boss He entrusted him with

587
00:27:53,400 --> 00:27:55,130
most of his business dealings.

588
00:27:55,440 --> 00:27:56,700
What kind of business?

589
00:28:01,000 --> 00:28:02,130
Logistics, I think.

590
00:28:03,340 --> 00:28:05,400
I don't really understand it either.

591
00:28:05,800 --> 00:28:06,360
Go on.

592
00:28:07,360 --> 00:28:09,680
Lai San, in order to
curry favor with Cheng,

593
00:28:09,680 --> 00:28:11,090
sent Meng Ling to him.

594
00:28:12,730 --> 00:28:13,860
Meng Ling told me...

595
00:28:15,950 --> 00:28:17,810
Cheng was a different kind of man.

596
00:28:18,490 --> 00:28:19,420
He treasured her

597
00:28:20,400 --> 00:28:22,270
and didn't treat her like a prostitute.

598
00:28:22,270 --> 00:28:24,870
Cheng even encouraged her
to go back to school,

599
00:28:25,840 --> 00:28:26,600
telling her

600
00:28:27,510 --> 00:28:29,770
that as long as one has determination...

601
00:28:30,750 --> 00:28:32,030
it's never too late.

602
00:28:32,800 --> 00:28:34,330
Meng Ling remembered that.

603
00:28:35,530 --> 00:28:37,900
She wrote it on her wall
and read it every day.

604
00:28:37,900 --> 00:28:40,300
What does that have to do
with Lai Zhengtian?

605
00:28:40,300 --> 00:28:41,690
Lai San sent Meng Ling

606
00:28:42,920 --> 00:28:44,050
to kiss up to Cheng,

607
00:28:45,310 --> 00:28:46,120
but Cheng

608
00:28:46,120 --> 00:28:47,780
didn't buy into his act at all.

609
00:28:48,600 --> 00:28:49,780
Once, when Lai San messed up

610
00:28:49,780 --> 00:28:51,920
a business deal for the logistics company,

611
00:28:51,920 --> 00:28:53,160
Cheng slapped him across the face

612
00:28:53,160 --> 00:28:54,360
in front of everyone.

613
00:28:54,800 --> 00:28:57,190
If Boss He hadn't stepped in at that time,

614
00:28:57,750 --> 00:28:59,330
those two would have fought,

615
00:28:59,330 --> 00:29:01,460
and one of them would surely have died.

616
00:29:01,790 --> 00:29:02,930
But not long after,

617
00:29:03,630 --> 00:29:06,030
Boss He transferred Cheng to another city,

618
00:29:06,510 --> 00:29:07,860
and he never came back.

619
00:29:09,240 --> 00:29:10,900
He could just leave like that,

620
00:29:12,390 --> 00:29:13,720
but Meng Ling couldn't.

621
00:29:17,620 --> 00:29:20,270
Lai San, having been humiliated,

622
00:29:22,270 --> 00:29:23,800
took it all out on Meng Ling.

623
00:29:26,160 --> 00:29:26,990
I swear,

624
00:29:28,480 --> 00:29:29,740
if Meng Ling is dead...

625
00:29:31,830 --> 00:29:33,690
Lai San is definitely the killer.

626
00:29:34,730 --> 00:29:37,460
What's the full name of this Cheng
you mentioned?

627
00:29:39,340 --> 00:29:40,100
Jiang Cheng.

628
00:29:50,050 --> 00:29:53,030
[Jiang Cheng]

629
00:29:58,710 --> 00:29:59,640
Jiang Hansheng.

630
00:30:00,990 --> 00:30:02,120
Don't do that again.

631
00:30:02,940 --> 00:30:04,140
It's very dangerous.

632
00:30:20,490 --> 00:30:22,290
When did you start following me?

633
00:30:25,810 --> 00:30:27,610
That man was Jiang Cheng, right?

634
00:30:32,230 --> 00:30:33,130
I don't mind.

635
00:30:37,370 --> 00:30:39,170
There's nothing to worry about.

636
00:30:40,380 --> 00:30:41,910
We just ran into each other,

637
00:30:41,990 --> 00:30:43,790
and then

638
00:30:43,840 --> 00:30:45,770
some unpleasant things happened.

639
00:30:46,640 --> 00:30:48,370
You don't need to explain to me.

640
00:30:54,790 --> 00:30:55,320
Zhou Jin.

641
00:30:56,990 --> 00:30:58,230
Stay here tonight,

642
00:30:58,680 --> 00:30:59,360
okay?

643
00:31:05,410 --> 00:31:08,140
I still have some clothes
I haven't brought over—

644
00:31:08,400 --> 00:31:09,880
pajamas and such...

645
00:31:09,880 --> 00:31:10,550
Wear mine.

646
00:31:16,680 --> 00:31:17,600
I need you.

647
00:31:31,620 --> 00:31:34,700
♪ Across the mountain ♪

648
00:31:35,060 --> 00:31:38,120
♪ A lonely boat waits ♪

649
00:31:38,330 --> 00:31:41,280
♪ Is it there ♪

650
00:31:41,810 --> 00:31:44,780
♪ For you to come ashore? ♪

651
00:31:45,270 --> 00:31:48,080
♪ Your questions ♪

652
00:31:48,680 --> 00:31:51,530
♪ I dare not ask ♪

653
00:31:52,000 --> 00:31:54,790
♪ If I did, I fear ♪

654
00:31:55,440 --> 00:31:58,320
♪ I'd throw caution to the wind for you ♪

655
00:31:58,830 --> 00:32:01,840
♪ The night is dark ♪

656
00:32:02,230 --> 00:32:05,270
♪ Dawn or dusk ♪

657
00:32:05,640 --> 00:32:09,180
♪ I don't want past memories ♪

658
00:32:09,380 --> 00:32:11,850
♪ To run wild again ♪

659
00:32:12,300 --> 00:32:15,320
♪ It was you who pushed open ♪

660
00:32:15,340 --> 00:32:17,770
♪ The door to my heart ♪

661
00:32:18,730 --> 00:32:22,020
♪ And now ♪

662
00:32:22,580 --> 00:32:25,710
♪ We're both more serious than before ♪

663
00:32:26,030 --> 00:32:28,600
♪ You've become ♪

664
00:32:28,620 --> 00:32:31,770
♪ My guiding star ♪

665
00:32:32,250 --> 00:32:37,770
♪ I don't want to dwell on ♪

666
00:32:39,010 --> 00:32:42,270
♪ The endless ticking of time ♪

667
00:32:42,300 --> 00:32:45,520
♪ My longing for you runs deep ♪

668
00:32:45,820 --> 00:32:48,770
♪ In that wavering moment ♪

669
00:32:49,760 --> 00:32:55,610
♪ Every door of my heart opens wide ♪

670
00:33:08,570 --> 00:33:09,230
Good night.

671
00:33:51,180 --> 00:33:51,960
What...

672
00:33:52,470 --> 00:33:54,120
book were you just reading?

673
00:33:56,050 --> 00:33:57,250
The Lord of the Rings.

674
00:33:58,900 --> 00:33:59,990
I hear the movies

675
00:34:01,190 --> 00:34:02,720
based on it are really good.

676
00:34:07,940 --> 00:34:08,540
Zhou Jin?

677
00:34:10,010 --> 00:34:11,010
Let's go to sleep.

678
00:34:29,290 --> 00:34:29,820
Zhou Jin?

679
00:34:54,790 --> 00:34:55,520
Are you okay?

680
00:34:55,830 --> 00:34:56,989
I'm fine. You?

681
00:34:59,600 --> 00:35:00,730
We're both wounded.

682
00:35:12,820 --> 00:35:13,750
Jiang Hansheng.

683
00:35:18,730 --> 00:35:19,460
You seem...

684
00:35:19,850 --> 00:35:20,850
different today.

685
00:35:23,410 --> 00:35:24,080
Really?

686
00:35:34,490 --> 00:35:35,200
Zhou Jin.

687
00:35:37,780 --> 00:35:39,240
Thank you for marrying me.

688
00:35:44,620 --> 00:35:46,280
Your heart is beating so fast.

689
00:35:49,920 --> 00:35:50,440
No way.

690
00:35:51,750 --> 00:35:53,480
I have a low resting heart rate.

691
00:35:57,330 --> 00:35:58,330
You...

692
00:36:00,750 --> 00:36:01,810
smell really nice.

693
00:36:04,170 --> 00:36:04,810
Do I?

694
00:36:19,100 --> 00:36:20,540
Do I smell nicer than him?

695
00:37:05,430 --> 00:37:06,070
Zhou Jin.

696
00:37:07,360 --> 00:37:08,160
You're awake.

697
00:37:09,100 --> 00:37:10,160
What are you doing?

698
00:37:11,790 --> 00:37:13,920
I'm writing a self-criticism report.

699
00:37:16,160 --> 00:37:17,620
Taking medicine so early?

700
00:37:17,910 --> 00:37:18,440
It hurts.

701
00:37:19,070 --> 00:37:19,950
Are those

702
00:37:20,110 --> 00:37:21,070
painkillers?

703
00:37:26,590 --> 00:37:27,900
Then don't take them on an empty stomach.

704
00:37:27,900 --> 00:37:28,830
Have some bread.

705
00:37:31,410 --> 00:37:32,610
My ribs hurt a bit too.

706
00:37:36,170 --> 00:37:37,300
You don't need this.

707
00:37:40,310 --> 00:37:40,970
Wait for me.

708
00:37:58,200 --> 00:37:59,200
You can take this.

709
00:38:05,680 --> 00:38:07,880
You didn't even ask what medicine it is.

710
00:38:09,200 --> 00:38:10,800
You wouldn't harm me anyway.

711
00:38:14,300 --> 00:38:15,500
Finally finished it.

712
00:38:17,600 --> 00:38:18,130
Alright,

713
00:38:18,160 --> 00:38:19,420
I need to go to work now.

714
00:38:20,460 --> 00:38:21,590
Is something wrong?

715
00:38:21,660 --> 00:38:23,660
You're not uncomfortable, are you?

716
00:38:23,870 --> 00:38:26,330
How's the case investigation progressing?

717
00:38:29,200 --> 00:38:30,560
We've already confirmed with the coroner

718
00:38:30,560 --> 00:38:32,830
that there are indeed no drag marks
on Meng Ling's body.

719
00:38:32,830 --> 00:38:34,040
Just as you said that day,

720
00:38:34,040 --> 00:38:35,710
if Lai San really committed the crime,

721
00:38:35,710 --> 00:38:36,920
he must have had an accomplice

722
00:38:36,920 --> 00:38:38,420
to help dispose of the body.

723
00:38:38,420 --> 00:38:39,420
The crime scene is

724
00:38:39,510 --> 00:38:41,390
quite far from downtown,

725
00:38:41,470 --> 00:38:43,080
so they must have used a vehicle.

726
00:38:43,080 --> 00:38:44,630
So the first thing we need to check

727
00:38:44,630 --> 00:38:45,580
is all the vehicles

728
00:38:45,580 --> 00:38:46,980
under Lai San's control.

729
00:38:47,440 --> 00:38:48,670
As for Lai San himself,

730
00:38:48,670 --> 00:38:50,040
we've already interrogated him once.

731
00:38:50,040 --> 00:38:51,420
He lives up to his reputation—

732
00:38:51,420 --> 00:38:52,750
he's truly a scoundrel.

733
00:38:53,420 --> 00:38:55,830
Lai San has strong psychological defenses.

734
00:38:55,830 --> 00:38:57,560
Don't waste time trying to
get him to confess.

735
00:38:57,560 --> 00:38:58,310
I suggest

736
00:38:58,660 --> 00:39:00,560
investigating his personal relationships—

737
00:39:00,560 --> 00:39:02,530
who he's close to
and who he has conflicts with.

738
00:39:02,530 --> 00:39:03,660
Find his weak spots.

739
00:39:05,120 --> 00:39:06,580
I'm going to Phoenix Fire.

740
00:39:10,210 --> 00:39:10,740
Zhou Jin.

741
00:39:13,870 --> 00:39:14,930
Going there again?

742
00:39:15,310 --> 00:39:16,370
Wanna come with me?

743
00:39:17,780 --> 00:39:18,510
I have class.

744
00:39:19,480 --> 00:39:20,540
Then I'll go ahead.

745
00:39:23,170 --> 00:39:24,170
Professor Jiang,

746
00:39:24,310 --> 00:39:26,170
anything else you need to tell me?

747
00:39:29,020 --> 00:39:29,500
No.

748
00:39:30,450 --> 00:39:31,510
I'll be going then.

749
00:39:50,460 --> 00:39:51,460
Professor Jiang,

750
00:39:51,630 --> 00:39:52,960
how is your injury?

751
00:39:53,520 --> 00:39:54,120
Chief Tan,

752
00:39:54,800 --> 00:39:56,180
are most of Lai Zhengtian's connections

753
00:39:56,180 --> 00:39:57,510
in Phoenix Fire?

754
00:39:57,720 --> 00:39:58,050
Yes.

755
00:39:58,570 --> 00:39:59,370
What's wrong?

756
00:40:00,620 --> 00:40:03,220
Zhou Jin's already gone
to do the questioning.

757
00:40:03,750 --> 00:40:04,880
We're on our way too.

758
00:40:05,880 --> 00:40:06,680
You all going?

759
00:40:06,790 --> 00:40:07,310
What?

760
00:40:08,060 --> 00:40:09,190
Are you free to come?

761
00:40:10,880 --> 00:40:12,390
I still have class this morning.

762
00:40:12,390 --> 00:40:13,860
Zhou Jin is already on her way.

763
00:40:13,860 --> 00:40:15,460
I just wanted to let you know.

764
00:40:15,980 --> 00:40:16,480
Okay.

765
00:40:17,110 --> 00:40:19,300
I'll contact you if anything comes up.

766
00:40:52,830 --> 00:40:53,230
Cheng!

767
00:40:53,310 --> 00:40:53,710
Cheng!

768
00:40:53,800 --> 00:40:54,200
Cheng!

769
00:40:54,440 --> 00:40:54,840
Cheng!

770
00:40:54,980 --> 00:40:55,560
Cheng!

771
00:40:55,590 --> 00:40:56,560
Cheng!

772
00:40:56,580 --> 00:40:57,200
Cheng!

773
00:41:05,230 --> 00:41:06,230
Officers,

774
00:41:06,560 --> 00:41:08,520
why don't you take these people back
for questioning?

775
00:41:08,520 --> 00:41:09,260
Can you do that?

776
00:41:09,260 --> 00:41:10,130
Your cars are all parked at the entrance.

777
00:41:10,130 --> 00:41:11,930
How am I supposed to do business?

778
00:41:13,590 --> 00:41:15,190
This is standard procedure.

779
00:41:15,310 --> 00:41:17,110
Please cooperate with our work.

780
00:41:17,620 --> 00:41:18,280
Cooperate.

781
00:41:18,560 --> 00:41:19,220
Cooperate.

782
00:41:19,880 --> 00:41:21,500
Cooperate properly. You hear that?

783
00:41:21,500 --> 00:41:22,850
-Got it!
-Got it!

784
00:41:24,230 --> 00:41:24,750
Cheng.

785
00:41:25,400 --> 00:41:26,080
Chief Tan.

786
00:41:26,790 --> 00:41:28,790
Gather everyone
who's familiar with Lai Zhengtian

787
00:41:28,790 --> 00:41:30,190
and bring them together.

788
00:41:30,350 --> 00:41:31,550
Take them back first.

789
00:41:31,640 --> 00:41:32,000
Yes.

790
00:41:32,030 --> 00:41:32,600
Yes.

791
00:41:33,040 --> 00:41:34,970
Take all relevant personnel away!

792
00:41:39,930 --> 00:41:42,160
The Captain of the Criminal Investigation Brigade
leading the team himself.

793
00:41:42,160 --> 00:41:44,980
Looks like someone
committed quite a serious crime.

794
00:41:44,980 --> 00:41:45,980
What's your name?

795
00:41:48,350 --> 00:41:49,080
Jiang Cheng.

796
00:41:51,680 --> 00:41:52,610
Nice to meet you.

797
00:41:57,140 --> 00:41:58,400
Did you know Meng Ling?

798
00:41:59,000 --> 00:41:59,600
Yes, I did.

799
00:41:59,990 --> 00:42:01,310
What was your relationship?

800
00:42:01,310 --> 00:42:02,960
We didn't have any relationship.

801
00:42:02,960 --> 00:42:04,420
According to what we know,

802
00:42:04,500 --> 00:42:05,730
you dated her.

803
00:42:07,160 --> 00:42:08,090
Were you lovers?

804
00:42:08,480 --> 00:42:09,750
Well, that depends on how your police

805
00:42:09,750 --> 00:42:11,390
define "lovers."

806
00:42:11,680 --> 00:42:14,230
If sleeping together a few times counts,

807
00:42:14,710 --> 00:42:16,710
then I'd have too many girlfriends.

808
00:42:17,440 --> 00:42:18,790
I see, I see.

809
00:42:20,250 --> 00:42:23,210
Just tell me yes or no.

810
00:42:28,090 --> 00:42:28,690
Chief Tan.

811
00:42:30,920 --> 00:42:31,780
No, we weren't.

812
00:42:32,440 --> 00:42:33,570
I have a girlfriend,

813
00:42:33,920 --> 00:42:35,080
and we're engaged.

814
00:42:36,510 --> 00:42:38,180
Since you knew Meng Ling...

815
00:42:42,380 --> 00:42:44,180
Did she ever mention in private

816
00:42:44,570 --> 00:42:45,900
whether she had grudges

817
00:42:46,390 --> 00:42:47,720
against Lai Zhengtian?

818
00:42:47,960 --> 00:42:48,560
No.

819
00:42:49,520 --> 00:42:50,580
What about Lai San?

820
00:42:51,000 --> 00:42:52,000
Did you notice...

821
00:42:53,350 --> 00:42:54,750
anyone threatening him?

822
00:42:57,120 --> 00:42:58,750
Whether Meng Ling
and Lai San had any conflicts,

823
00:42:58,750 --> 00:43:00,010
I honestly don't know.

824
00:43:00,680 --> 00:43:01,980
But if you're asking who in this place

825
00:43:01,980 --> 00:43:03,710
has the biggest grudge against Lai San,

826
00:43:03,710 --> 00:43:04,520
that would definitely be me.
